1
00:01:01,560 --> 00:01:02,000
Shh.

2
00:01:13,560 --> 00:01:14,519
You're back.

3
00:01:19,719 --> 00:01:21,040
I heard you didn't eat.

4
00:01:21,599 --> 00:01:22,680
I'm not hungry.

5
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:24,959
You still need to eat.

6
00:01:25,519 --> 00:01:27,319
You need nutrients now.

7
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:32,200
Lie down.

8
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:43,079
I'll get you something to eat.

9
00:01:52,519 --> 00:01:53,000
No.

10
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:53,760
I don't want to eat.

11
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:55,159
Eat a little.

12
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,560
I'm not hungry.

13
00:01:58,319 --> 00:01:59,319
Drink a little.

14
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:01,680
I think you are hungry.

15
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:08,520
Is it good?

16
00:04:41,079 --> 00:04:41,560
Master

17
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:43,399
Mr. Shen asked you to go back with me.

18
00:04:43,399 --> 00:04:44,199
It's too late.

19
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,160
I have to stay with Qi.

20
00:04:47,199 --> 00:04:47,839
He wants to see me.

21
00:04:49,079 --> 00:04:50,000
Let him come himself.

22
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:51,720
Master

23
00:04:52,759 --> 00:04:53,240
Shen Yu

24
00:04:53,639 --> 00:04:53,959
Yes.

25
00:05:05,439 --> 00:05:06,000
Yellow.

26
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:08,920
Cyan.

27
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:11,839
Red.

28
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:13,720
Black.

29
00:05:16,639 --> 00:05:17,279
Orange.

30
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,199
Cyan and green

31
00:05:20,199 --> 00:05:21,040
are a little hard to distinguish.

32
00:05:21,199 --> 00:05:21,800
It doesn't matter.

33
00:05:22,079 --> 00:05:23,480
At present, the recovery is still okay.

34
00:05:24,279 --> 00:05:25,639
I can still see clearly, right?

35
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:26,480
Yes.

36
00:05:26,639 --> 00:05:27,680
I can't guarantee this to you.

37
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,279
But this is the most optimistic result.

38
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,680
I'm satisfied as long as there is hope.

39
00:05:33,319 --> 00:05:34,240
The family should also be positive.

40
00:05:34,639 --> 00:05:36,279
The patient is in a better mood than you.

41
00:05:37,279 --> 00:05:37,720
Thank you.

42
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:44,639
Jiang Yue

43
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:46,920
I saw it that day.

44
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:48,720
it was Chu Mo who fired the gun.

45
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,639
I didn't listen to you

46
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:53,839
when you warned me.

47
00:05:54,439 --> 00:05:55,639
I was not careful enough.

48
00:05:56,519 --> 00:05:57,319
I'm sorry.

49
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,000
I dislike Chu Mo.

50
00:06:00,519 --> 00:06:01,519
But he didn't fire the gun.

51
00:06:03,199 --> 00:06:04,000
Who did?

52
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:06,279
You know?

53
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:11,120
No matter who it is,

54
00:06:11,439 --> 00:06:12,439
it's not your fault.

55
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:13,439
It's okay.

56
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:16,279
Let's go.

57
00:06:17,319 --> 00:06:18,160
Let's go out for a walk.

58
00:07:08,759 --> 00:07:11,199
You've been with me for so many days.

59
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:13,680
Is everything okay with uncle?

60
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:14,199
It's okay.

61
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:19,600
I know why you

62
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,839
have to obey him.

63
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,399
I'm okay.

64
00:07:24,399 --> 00:07:25,319
Don't give him

65
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:27,439
the chance to hurt you because of me.

66
00:07:30,199 --> 00:07:31,639
You once asked me

67
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:35,000
how I want to live my life.

68
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,160
Yes.

69
00:07:36,160 --> 00:07:36,639
I thought about it.

70
00:07:39,439 --> 00:07:40,759
I devoted everything I had before

71
00:07:40,759 --> 00:07:42,040
to a lie.

72
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:44,920
That lie is like a gun

73
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:46,240
pointing at my heart.

74
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:48,399
My fate

75
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:50,839
is in the hands of a gun holder

76
00:07:51,839 --> 00:07:53,040
who doesn't love me.

77
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:55,720
But after I met you,

78
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:56,600
I figured it out.

79
00:07:57,319 --> 00:07:58,560
I won't allow anyone in this world

80
00:07:58,560 --> 00:07:59,639
to hurt you,

81
00:08:00,879 --> 00:08:02,240
and no one will hurt me.

82
00:08:04,439 --> 00:08:05,560
If I have to choose,

83
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:08,680
I'd rather the person who hurts me is you.

84
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:36,200
Changfa,

85
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:38,320
I'm so worried about Qi.

86
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,080
Just let me go.

87
00:08:41,039 --> 00:08:41,960
What can you do here?

88
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:43,320
Wait at home.

89
00:08:57,039 --> 00:08:57,679
What did you say?

90
00:08:58,600 --> 00:08:59,559
Miss is alone.

91
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:00,840
So, Master...

92
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:12,120
Call ASO here.

93
00:09:36,399 --> 00:09:38,159
Qi Qi, Qi Qi.

94
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:40,879
Qi Qi.

95
00:09:48,759 --> 00:09:49,720
The medicine the doctor sent

96
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:51,840
was switched.

97
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:52,960
I'll call for help.

98
00:09:54,159 --> 00:09:54,399
No need.

99
00:10:02,320 --> 00:10:02,759
There's no time.

100
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:04,919
Contact the dock

101
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:06,120
and prepare for the reception.

102
00:10:06,759 --> 00:10:07,039
Yes.

103
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:19,679
Master, go now.

104
00:10:38,759 --> 00:10:39,120
Master.

105
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:40,080
Sorry.

106
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:40,759
Go.
